=== 服裝缺乏識別 ===
{{main|香港警隊委任證爭議|禁止蒙面規例}}
從特別戰術小隊成立至2016年間，特別戰術小隊的制服會展示警員編號及職級。然而[[反修例運動|反修例運動]]期間，特別戰術小隊的服裝不再展示有關資料，被批評缺乏身份。[[李家超|李家超]]回應指小隊的服裝沒有足夠空間展示警員編號<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/342330/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E9%84%BA%E4%BF%8A%E5%AE%87%E6%89%B9%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A%E9%9A%B1%E8%97%8F%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%99%9F%E7%A2%BC-%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85-%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D%E7%84%A1%E4%BD%8D|title=【逃犯條例】鄺俊宇批速龍小隊隱藏警員號碼　李家超：制服無位|date=2019-06-19|work=香港01|accessdate=2020-07-28|archive-date=2019-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190620133103/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/342330/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E9%84%BA%E4%BF%8A%E5%AE%87%E6%89%B9%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A%E9%9A%B1%E8%97%8F%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%99%9F%E7%A2%BC-%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85-%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D%E7%84%A1%E4%BD%8D|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[李柱銘|李柱銘]]認為有關說法不合理，並舉例指選美參加者身穿比堅尼仍有足夠空間展示號碼<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/490248/%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%B7%A8%E8%99%9F%E6%A1%88-%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%BD%98%E7%86%99-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%80%9A%E4%BE%8B-%E6%8C%87%E5%BC%95%E5%B7%B2%E5%81%9C%E7%94%A8|title=司法覆核警員編號案　資深大律師潘熙：《警察通例》指引已停用|date=2020-06-24|work=香港01|accessdate=2020-07-28|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728061722/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/490248/%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%B7%A8%E8%99%9F%E6%A1%88-%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%BD%98%E7%86%99-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%80%9A%E4%BE%8B-%E6%8C%87%E5%BC%95%E5%B7%B2%E5%81%9C%E7%94%A8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[監警會|監警會]]於2020年5月發表的報告表示小隊的裝束不屬《[[警察通例|警察通例]]》規管的制服。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/473810/%E7%9B%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E6%9C%AA%E8%A7%A3%E7%AD%94%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E5%91%BC%E8%99%9F%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0-%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%8B%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E5%BD%88%E7%99%BC%E5%B0%84%E5%AE%88%E5%89%87|title=監警會報告｜未解答速龍小隊行動呼號爭議　不見防暴彈發射守則|date=2020-05-16|work=香港01|accessdate=2020-07-28|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728020311/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/473810/%E7%9B%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E6%9C%AA%E8%A7%A3%E7%AD%94%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E5%91%BC%E8%99%9F%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0-%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%8B%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E5%BD%88%E7%99%BC%E5%B0%84%E5%AE%88%E5%89%87|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[周家明|周家明]]法官於關於警員展示編號一事的司法覆核中質疑包括特別戰術小隊在內的警員隱藏身份的原因，並指法官和檢控官的身份亦同樣是對公眾公開。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/490987/%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%B7%A8%E8%99%9F%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E6%A1%88-%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%AD%A6%E6%86%82%E9%81%AD%E5%A0%B1%E5%BE%A9%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95-%E5%AE%98%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E4%B9%9F%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA|title=警員編號覆核案｜律師指警憂遭報復起底　官稱司法人員也面對風險|date=2020-06-26|work=香港01|accessdate=2020-07-28|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728021929/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/490987/%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%B7%A8%E8%99%9F%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E6%A1%88-%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%AD%A6%E6%86%82%E9%81%AD%E5%A0%B1%E5%BE%A9%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95-%E5%AE%98%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E4%B9%9F%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA|dead-url=no}}</ref>

